<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="pm_bank_logo.jpg" />
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>PM BANK</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #000;
            color: white;
            background-image: url('pm_bank_logo.jpg');
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center 300px;
            background-size: 400px;
            opacity: 0.98;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #111;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
        }
        header img {
            height: 60px;
        }
        nav a {
            color: white;
            margin-left: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #FFD700;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #ccc;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background-color: #0077FF;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #111;
            margin-top: 80px;
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <img src=\"pm_bank_logo.jpg\" alt="PM BANK Logo">
    <nav>
        <a href="#">Inicio</a>
        <a href="#">Servicios</a>
        <a href="#">App</a>
        <a href="#">Contacto</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
    <img src="pm_bank_logo.jpg" alt="PM BANK Logo" style="height:120px; margin-bottom:20px;">
    <h1>Bienvenido a PM BANK</h1>
    <p>Pagos instantáneos. Transferencias por QR. Sin tarjetas. Sin fricción.</p>
    <a class="btn" href="#">Crear Cuenta</a>
</section>

<footer>
    <img src="pm_bank_logo.jpg" alt="PM BANK Logo" style="height:60px; display:block; margin:0 auto 10px auto;">
    © 2025 PM BANK — Todos los derechos reservados.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
